risk: Moves a lot with the market
explain: Stock‑specific: after removing market moves, drawdown is ~0% (more extreme than 3% of days).
Drawdown: 1% below its 1‑year high (more extreme than 2% of past days).
Range: in the bottom 99% of its 1‑year range (only 99% of days were this low‑in‑range or lower).
